claim.claim-text:
1. A group-III nitride crystal growth apparatus comprising:
a mixed molten liquid container holding a mixed molten liquid of an alkaline metal and a substance at least containing a group-III metal;
a reaction vessel having said mixed molten liquid container set therein;
a device introducing a substance at least containing nitrogen into said reaction vessel; and
an observation device through which the inside of said reaction vessel is observable, said observation device comprising a transparent window provided in said reaction vessel,
wherein said transparent window has a film of a group-III nitride provided on the inner surface thereof.

14. A group-III nitride crystal growth apparatus comprising:
a mixed molten liquid container provided in a reaction vessel and in which a mixed molten liquid of an alkaline material and a substance at least containing a group-III metal is formed, growth of a group-III nitride crystal being caused from the mixed molten liquid and a substance at least containing nitrogen;
a material container provided outside of said reaction vessel, from which the substance at least containing the group-III metal is fed into the inside of said reaction vessel due to the self gravity of said substance at least containing the group-III metal;
a pressure adjustment pipe providing communication between said mixed molten liquid container and said material container;
a supply pipe also providing communication between said mixed molten liquid container and said material container; and
a device controlling the mutual height relationship between said mixed molten liquid container and said material container.
